1766Nasampayuttapaccayā nahetupaccayā (mūlakaṃ saṃkhittaṃ) nasahajātapaccayā naaññamaññapaccayā nanissayapaccayā upanissaye nava, pacchājāte tīṇi, kamme dve, āhāre ekaṃ, indriye ekaṃ, vippayutte tīṇi, atthiyā pañca, avigate pañca…pe… .
